Provide group lookup compatibility entry points in AgentOS wasi-libc.

Tree links getgrgid() for optional `-g` group-name output. AgentOS VMs expose
numeric gid/getgroups behavior but do not project a group database, so group
name lookups should fail deterministically and let callers fall back to numeric
gids.

